WEBVTT

11:04.710 --> 11:06.710 line:80%
Auntie Zhao, help me get him inside.

11:06.760 --> 11:07.160 line:80%
You...

11:07.830 --> 11:09.120 line:80%
You don't even know if he's good or bad,

11:09.120 --> 11:10.650 line:80%
yet you dare bring him home?

11:10.800 --> 11:11.930 line:80%
Besides, he is a man.

11:12.190 --> 11:13.710 line:80%
You're an unmarried girl.

11:14.120 --> 11:15.920 line:80%
People's gossip will drown you!
